:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353dded68d2538764dad19da1fc97e8a4d754353","tid":1810242,"uid":198355,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"中車加速度高 又涼 好過英國車又熱 係事實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"屌你原本係用緊西班牙同泡菜車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東涌綫啲車出名通風好"},{"pid":"008840a0d5062d883a02ed93ab0e54d901c63e4e","tid":1810242,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"d支那人成日話冇收香港税<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9bb79028722b37bdb668db630eb6a68ac11885","tid":1810242,"uid":59552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"大家唔好忘記當年點解買入西班牙車係因為大陸cut左英國佬既預算<br />\n<br />\n其實西班牙車老化得好快，車架裂痕，車架變形，無維修零件等<br />\n車門同車框已經頂唔順，換左好多大陸野<br />\n車底又有裂紋<br />\n<br />\n利申：發up瘋"},{"pid":"8f0b6bb7af02bc6e13b67ffe5cb572864fac1366","tid":1810242,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3aa1c84d4fb814dab92de32c735eb108efd14941","tid":1810242,"uid":77547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a65abf31e5cc1d96b343d8165328fb5fb0ce2eb8","tid":1810242,"uid":38795,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/516AGHr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F516AGHr.jpg&h=bbafd44b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"奶得黎，其實港鐵響大陸都係俾人用完即棄。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"棄緊啦<br />\n幫傻西仲以為係上面有得玩返香港地鐵站上蓋送你起樓呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你港鐵咩新鮮蘿蔔皮啊？condom咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}